<div id="review_2350959806" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2350959806" />
    <a title="Vikas Singh" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/23007922-vikas-singh"><img alt="Vikas Singh" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1591592210p2/23007922.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2350959806?book_show_action=true">Apr 04, 2018</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Vikas Singh" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Vikas Singh" href="/user/show/23007922-vikas-singh">Vikas Singh</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/23007922-vikas-singh?shelf=owned-book">owned-book</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2350959806" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7012089563843391553">It is a collection of nine stories. One of these feature Hercule Poirot. So strictly speaking it is not a Poirot collection. There are some love stories with love triangles and some supernatural stories. But my favourite is Manx Gold, which was an unique attempt to promote tourism in the Isle of Man. Agatha Christie wrote this story on a commission and it was supplemented by clues published in newspaper promoting a treasure hunt. Unique idea.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

