<span id="freeTextContainer16869422695855334541">-The House of Dreams: ⭐️⭐️⭐️<br/>-The Actress: ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️<br/>-The Edge: ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️<br/>-Christmas Adventure: ⭐️⭐️⭐️<br/>-The Lonely God: ⭐️⭐️<br/>-Manx Gold: ⭐️⭐️.5<br/>-The Mystery of the Baghdad Chest: ⭐️⭐️⭐️.5<br/>-While the Light Lasts: ⭐️⭐️<br/><br/>I liked that this edition included an afterword after each short story. It was a fun way to learn more about the short story that came before it and the history begin any previous publications of it. Overall, a solid read that got me back in the mood for more Agatha Christie, so 4 stars!</span>

