        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2556763662" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6314621573792372316">now i am hooked. This was such a great, easy and creative book. i was hooked after the first page. <br/><br/>The characters were easy to fall in love with and follow, along with the story. the author made the mental visions so easy and vivid of the surroundings and the characters actions felt so real.<br/><br/>i would highly recommend this author and this book.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


